<note id="fs-idm174044896" class="os-teacher">
<title>Facilitation Notes</title>
<para id="fs-idm177445072">After students have analyzed the excerpts provided, inform the class that the South Carolina House of Representatives took no action on the <emphasis effect="italics">South Carolina Exposition and Protest</emphasis>. Thousands of copies of Calhoun’s pamphlet were printed and distributed across the state. You might follow up with this question: To what extent is this document significant, in light of the fact that that it was written anonymously and failed to achieve official support by the South Carolina legislature?</para>
