<section id="fs-idm294371040">
<title>Comprehension Questions</title>
<exercise id="fs-idm220239296">
<problem id="fs-idm160705664">
<para id="fs-idm205779440">According to this argument, the Tariff of 1828 was unconstitutional because of its purpose. What is the difference between a tariff whose purpose is to raise revenue to pay for public expenses, and a tariff whose purpose is to protect domestic industry from foreign competition?</para>
</problem>
</exercise>
<exercise id="fs-idm220142448">
<problem id="fs-idm209682320">
